    <tr> 
      <td align="left"> <font face=verdana><b>Sheffield Actionnaires (Former Name)</b></font><br> </td>
    </tr>


    
   <tr>
   <td align="left">
   <font face=verdana>Action For Blind People is a registered charity that runs a free activity club for blind and partially sighted children aged 4-16 years.  Sports and activities include:<br>• climbing<br>• trampolining<br>• street dance<br>• swimming<br>• goal ball<br><br>Meets at the Westfield Sports Centre, S20 (Sunday).<br><br>Children under 8 years of age must be accompanied by an adult.  Siblings and friends are welcome to come along and join in all the activities.</font><BR></td></tr>


